data.description: A charming three-bedroom brick ranch nestled on a spacious lot, completely fenced for privacy. Located just minutes away from Joe Wheeler State Park and the scenic Tennessee River, this home offers easy access to HWY 72, as well as a plethora of shopping, dining, and healthcare options.
